These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, milk, almond-milk, 7up, coffee
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, horse, goldfish, dog, rabbit
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the owner of the horse is the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
12. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |    3     |  4   |       5       |   6   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | water    | mirinda | milk | 7up |
| Pet        | lizard      | rabbit  | goldfish | chinchilla | dog          | horse  |

