.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, soy-milk, sprite, cola, lemonade
There are 6 different nationalities: turkish, malaysian, dutch, brazilian, german, indonesian
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the turkish is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 4. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 5. the german is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the dutch##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 8. the indonesian is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the brazilian is on the right of the dutch##1
11. the german is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
12. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
13. the dutch is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
14. the dutch is on the left or right of the turkish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4     |     5     |    6     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | sprite     | iced-tea | soy-milk    | lemonade       | cola  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | turkish | dutch       | brazilian | malaysian | german |

