.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, water, iced-tea, cola, mirinda
The people have 6 different hobbies: sudoku, baking, filmmaking, singing, photography, hiking
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person drinking cola##2
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
10. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |       6       |
| Beverage   | almond-milk   | mirinda     | cola | sprite        | iced-tea   | water |
| Hobby      | sudoku | photography | filmmaking  | baking | hiking | singing       |

