3. the colombian is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
4. the british is the person eating mango##1
5. the argentine is on the far right##1
6. the indonesian is the person eating papaya##1
7. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the far left##1
9. the indonesian is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |     5     |    6     |
