.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-6::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  musician, pilot, chef, manager, videographer, dressmaker
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skiing, lacrosse, water-polo, parkour, handball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the musician##3
 2. the musician is between the person who's sport is parkour and the dressmaker##2
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the chef##1
 5. the manager is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 6. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
 7. the musician is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the manager is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 9. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the pilot is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |   2    |     3     |     4      |      5       |        6        |
| Job     | pilot        | manager | dressmaker | musician  | chef  | videographer |
| Sport   | water-polo | lacrosse   | skiing  | weightlifting | parkour | handball          |

