.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-7::.
6 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, cat, lizard, snake, bird
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, bus, helicopter, trike, taxi, car
 1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 4. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 6. the person driving the car is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the lizard and the person driving the bus##2
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |    3     |     4      |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | bird | cat      | lizard | snake | rat | rabbit |
| Transport   | bus  | boat | taxi   | car        | helicopter   | trike |

