 7. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
11. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
