 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3

